            <title>[SPR-177] PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer does not recognize default properties</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-177</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer correctly substitutes explcit properties of a Properties object but does not recignize default properties if those exist.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Junit test case is attached.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
